    <name>Distance Learning is Different ​</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{160}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Distance learning is not as simple as taking information that has been delivered in-person, uploading&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;it to an online platform and, calling it distance learning. Distance learning&amp;nbsp;has to&amp;nbsp;be carefully designed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to provide your learners with supports that make it easier for them to orient themselves to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;learning environment and&amp;nbsp;efficiently find the information they need on their own, with minimal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;effort&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Diep, 2019 and Forman &amp;amp; Chapman, 2021)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. Otherwise, your learners may become frustrated not by the content, but by the mechanics of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;navigating the course, and they may decide it is not worth their time.&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{163}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Ways you can create more inviting and supportive distance learning for adult learners include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul role="list"&gt;&lt;li data-margin="460" data-aria-posinset="1" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{166}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:460,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-450,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}" data-indent="-450"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Building social presence&amp;nbsp;to create a more friendly, inviting learning environment&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-margin="460" data-aria-posinset="2" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{169}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:460,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-450,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}" data-indent="-450"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Ensuring materials and technologies are accessible to all your learners&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-margin="460" data-aria-posinset="3" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{172}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:460,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-450,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}" data-indent="-450"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Organizing information to help learners find what they need, when they need it&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{175}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
